OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775664666
OL,3,CDonkey sanctuary describes 'soul-
OL,4,Cdestroying' abuse suffered by dumped
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FA Cumbrian donkey sanctuary says abuse
OL,8,Fof the animals is on the rise after
OL,9,F"one of the worst cases of abuse ever"
OL,10,Fwas dumped on their doorstep last
OL,11,Fmonth.
OL,13,FBarnhill Donkey's Retreat in Sleagill,
OL,14,Fnear Shap has had a dozen donkeys
OL,15,Fdumped at their door since December,
OL,16,Feffectively doubling the number of
OL,17,Fanimals they care for.
OL,19,FThree of these have been since March
OL,20,F19, including a donkey the vets named
OL,21,FMary.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
