FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775664666
OL,3,CDonkey sanctuary describes 'soul-
OL,4,Cdestroying' abuse suffered by dumped
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FWhen she was found, Mary was
OL,8,Femaciated, ridden with lice, with very
OL,9,Flittle hair remaining. Her skin was
OL,10,Fbleeding and she had an old crack in
OL,11,Fher pedal bone which is inside her
OL,12,Fhoof. She also had a four-inch abscess
OL,13,Funder her top teeth, meaning that she
OL,14,Fwas unable to eat.
OL,16,FLinda Gilbert, who runs the sanctuary,
OL,17,Fwas so alarmed by Mary's condition
OL,18,Fthat she rang the police.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775664666
OL,3,CDonkey sanctuary describes 'soul-
OL,4,Cdestroying' abuse suffered by dumped
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FShe told ITV Border: "How she survived
OL,8,Fthe winter is some form of miracle.
OL,9,FThis is actually soul destroying. It's
OL,10,Fsoul destroying what they're going
OL,11,Fthrough.
OL,13,F"Mary has to stand there and look at
OL,14,Ffood and not be able to eat it and
OL,15,Fslowly starve to death. She's
OL,16,Fterrified, even after 3 weeks, she's
OL,17,Fstill terrified.
OL,19,F"This is not normal. This is not
OL,20,Fhuman."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775664666
OL,3,CDonkey sanctuary describes 'soul-
OL,4,Cdestroying' abuse suffered by dumped
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FPreviously, ITV Border had reported on
OL,8,Fthe case of a donkey called Hope who
OL,9,Fwas abandoned at Barnhill Retreat in
OL,10,Fvery poor health.
OL,12,FDespite recovering from anaemia over
OL,13,Fthe Christmas period, Hope died in
OL,14,FFebruary.
OL,16,FLinda says she believes the rise in
OL,17,Fabuse cases is due to people not
OL,18,Fknowing how to properly take care of
OL,19,Fdonkeys they buy.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
