PN,35805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775664666
OL,3,CDonkey sanctuary describes 'soul-
OL,4,Cdestroying' abuse suffered by dumped
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FShe said: "I think it's indifference.
OL,8,FI think when the donkeys take ill,
OL,9,Frather than getting the vet, they just
OL,10,Fput them in a corner and leave them
OL,11,Fthere.
OL,13,F"It's only when it gets to the point
OL,14,Fthat they think someone is going to
OL,15,Freport them, they think 'let's get rid
OL,16,Fof it' and they dump it. They don't
OL,17,Fcare."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
