PN,35806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775664666
OL,3,CDonkey sanctuary describes 'soul-
OL,4,Cdestroying' abuse suffered by dumped
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FThe influx of dumped donkeys has
OL,8,Fprompted the Barnhill Donkey Sanctuary
OL,9,Fto increase the scope of its planned
OL,10,Fexpansion in order to cope with the
OL,11,Fnew arrivals.
OL,13,FWork that was going to extend their
OL,14,Fstable yard next month will now treble
OL,15,Fthe size of the stabling space at
OL,16,Fenormous cost to the charity.
OL,18,FLinda says: "We're desperate for
OL,19,Ffunding like every rescuer is. This is
OL,20,Fgoing to cost us about #15,000 because
OL,21,Fwe're getting so many donkeys in now.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
