PN,35807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1775664666
OL,3,CDonkey sanctuary describes 'soul-
OL,4,Cdestroying' abuse suffered by dumped
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,F"The donkeys do amazing things for our
OL,8,Fcommunity. We have Shap Primary
OL,9,FSchool, we have playgroups, we have
OL,10,Fdisability groups. The donkeys give a
OL,11,Flot and they don't ask for anything
OL,12,Fback so we've decided to treble the
OL,13,Fstable yard and nothing will be turned
OL,14,Faway."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
